## About Page

간단히 About 페이지를 만들어 봅시다.

about 페이지와 AboutCoverSection 컴포넌트를 생성 후 AboutCoverSection 컴포넌트를 about 페이지에 임포트 합니다.

```javascript title="src/app/about/page.js"
import AboutCoverSection from "@/src/components/About/AboutCoverSection";

const About = () => {
  return (
    <div>
      <AboutCoverSection />
    </div>
  );
};

export default About;
```

```javascript title="src/components/About/AboutCoverSection.js"
import Image from "next/image";
import React from "react";
import profileCharater from "@/public/character.png";

const AboutCoverSection = () => {
  return (
    <section className="w-full h-[75vh] border-b-2 border-dark flex items-center justify-center text-dark">
      <div className="w-1/2 h-full border-r-2 border-dark flex justify-center">
        <Image
          src={profileCharater}
          alt="Baekki"
          className="w-full h-full object-contain object-center"
        />
      </div>

      <div className="w-1/2 flex flex-col justify-center px-16">
        <h2 className="font-bold capitalize text-6xl">
          Imagine Limitlessly, Strive Relentlessly, Surpass Expectations!
        </h2>
        <p className="font-medium capitalize mt-4">
          In the realms of blockchain and front-end development, I focus on
          redefining user experiences through innovative solutions. Working at
          the forefront of technology, I develop applications that enable
          efficient and secure digital transactions, harnessing the potential of
          blockchain technology. Simultaneously, by leveraging modern web
          technologies, I craft intuitive and visually appealing interfaces that
          allow users to navigate and interact with information effectively and
          seamlessly. If you have a project in mind, please reach out to me.
          Let's make it happen together.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>
  );
};

export default AboutCoverSection;
```

